<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Works_about_Foster">Works about Foster</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Author:Stephen_Collins_Foster&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Works about Foster"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<ul><li><span class="ws-authlink">"<a href="/wiki/A_Short_Biographical_Dictionary_of_English_Literature/Foster,_Stephen_Collins" title="A Short Biographical Dictionary of English Literature/Foster, Stephen Collins">Foster, Stephen Collins</a>," in <i><a href="/wiki/A_Short_Biographical_Dictionary_of_English_Literature" title="A Short Biographical Dictionary of English Literature">A Short Biographical Dictionary of English Literature</a></i>, by <a href="/wiki/Author:John_William_Cousin" title="Author:John William Cousin">John William Cousin</a>, London: J. M. Dent &amp; Sons&#32;(1910)</span></li>
